From Jonathan Polito Subject Re Aerostitch or piece In article writes Request for opinions Which is better a one piece Aerostitch or a two piece Aerostitch We're looking for more than Well the pc is more versatile but the pc is better protection Thanks in advance Nadine What is best Books have been written on that But in regard to AeroStich it really depends on your particular size shape and If you upper and lower body are not proportional according to aero dimensions then it probably is going to be better mixing and matching the piece I have the piece suit and I am very happy with Having my life quota of scars from crashing off road I am very concerned with good protection and I believe that the difference in protection between the and piece suits is almost I think the optional hip pads and back protector make much more of a One thing that is nice about the piece is if you go somewhere and then want to walk around for a while still with jacket you can just detach and stow the One thing to note is that Goldfine has problems getting a good fit for many women with standard suits Supposedly for smaller women and petite men for that matter the piece will fit Another recommendation is to pay for mods if you need I wish I got inches added to my pant I find the Long suits are not really that long I can't imagine how short the standard suits must be Jonathan Polito Internet Encore Computer Corp Kildaire Farm Rd Cary NC USA voice FAX